nhc_headline: ...JERRY CONTINUES MOVING QUICKLY WEST-NORTHWESTWARD... ...TROPICAL STORM WATCH IN EFFECT FOR PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS...
summary: ...JERRY CONTINUES MOVING QUICKLY WEST-NORTHWESTWARD... ...TROPICAL STORM WATCH IN EFFECT FOR PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS... As of 5:00 AM AST Wed Oct 08 the center of Jerry was located near 13.3, -50.7 with movement WNW at 23 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
